OL,3,CCalls for resignation over 'very short
OL,4,Cskirts' remark
OL,6,FA police boss is facing calls to
OL,7,Fresign over comments he made about
OL,8,Fschoolgirls wearing "very short
OL,9,Fskirts".
OL,11,FJohn Dwyer, Cheshire's Police and
OL,12,FCrime Commissioner, made the comments
OL,13,Fduring a discussion about violence and
OL,14,Fabuse of women and girls.
OL,16,FHe was reported to have told Culcheth
OL,17,Fand Glazebury parish council: "I
OL,18,Fnotice schoolgirls in my area are all
OL,19,Fwearing very short skirts and this did
OL,20,Fnot happen in the 1960s."
