OL,3,CCalls for resignation over 'very short
OL,4,Cskirts' remark
OL,6,FMr Dwyer has since issued an
OL,7,F"unreserved apology" for the remarks,
OL,8,Fbut there has been widespread
OL,9,Fcriticism of his comments and calls
OL,10,Ffor Mr Dwyer to step down.
OL,12,FCheshire West and Chester Council
OL,13,Fleader Louise Gittins said: "John
OL,14,FDwyer's comments were disgraceful and
OL,15,Fhis apology does not change the fact
OL,16,Fthat he thought it appropriate to
OL,17,Fcomment on the clothing of young girls
OL,18,Fand blame female victims of abuse and
OL,19,Ftrauma.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G2/10
