OL,3,CCalls for resignation over 'very short
OL,4,Cskirts' remark
OL,6,F"Mr Dwyer says one of his priorities
OL,7,Fis the safety of women and girls, then
OL,8,Fhe's come out with this sexist,
OL,9,Fmisogynistic, outdated comment which
OL,10,Fis victim-blaming," he said.
OL,12,F"Implying women and girls are
OL,13,Fresponsible for any unwanted attention
OL,14,Fif they wear a short skirt.
OL,16,F"He is setting the wrong example to
OL,17,Fthe men and women who work for
OL,18,FCheshire Constabulary given his
OL,19,Fimportant leadership and scrutiny role.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G4/10
