OL,3,CCalls for resignation over 'very short
OL,4,Cskirts' remark
OL,6,F"This episode also undermines public
OL,7,Fconfidence because victims may be
OL,8,Fdissuaded from coming forward if they
OL,9,Ffeel they won't be listened to.
OL,11,F"Mr Dwyer is supposed to be the one
OL,12,Fholding the force to account on behalf
OL,13,Fof the people of Cheshire yet how can
OL,14,Fhe be taken seriously after this? I
OL,15,Fcall on him to do the right thing and
OL,16,Fresign."
OL,18,FMr Dwyers comments were also condemned
OL,19,Fby the branch secretary of Unison
OL,20,Funion.
