OL,6,FThe Cheshire Police branch secretary
OL,7,Fof the Unison union, Joanne Moorcroft,
OL,8,Fsaid: "The misogynistic comments made
OL,9,Fby the Cheshire Police and Crime
OL,10,FCommissioner are very disappointing
OL,11,Fand have caused a lot of anger.
OL,13,F"This is particularly disheartening as
OL,14,FCheshire Police has made violence
OL,15,Fagainst women and girls a priority for
OL,16,Fthe force.
