OL,3,CCalls for resignation over 'very short
OL,4,Cskirts' remark
OL,6,F"Public confidence in policing is at
OL,7,Fan all-time low and forces' attitudes
OL,8,Fto sexism and racism are frequently
OL,9,Fcalled into question, despite some of
OL,10,Fthe great work staff do. Leaders
OL,11,Fshould lead by example, and these
OL,12,Freprehensible comments will only serve
OL,13,Fto further damage public trust in the
OL,14,Fforce and the morale of the staff
OL,15,Fworking in it."
