OL,3,CCalls for resignation over 'very short
OL,4,Cskirts' remark
OL,6,FIn a statement, Conservative Mr Dwyer,
OL,7,Fwho became Cheshire's first PCC in
OL,8,F2012, said: "I want to begin by
OL,9,Facknowledging the understandable hurt
OL,10,Fcaused, and to make it unequivocally
OL,11,Fclear that what I said was wrong.
OL,13,F"I would like to offer both the
OL,14,Fcomplainant and the Police and Crime
OL,15,FPanel a full and unreserved apology. I
OL,16,Fam truly sorry and accept that my
OL,17,Fcomment was inappropriate and
OL,18,Funhelpful.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G8/10
