OL,3,CCalls for resignation over 'very short
OL,4,Cskirts' remark
OL,6,F"In no way does it give an accurate
OL,7,Freflection of how seriously I take the
OL,8,Fmatter of tackling Violence Against
OL,9,FWomen and Girls (VAWG). There can be
OL,10,Fno justification for the actions of
OL,11,Fperpetrators.
OL,13,F"My ambition to tackle this issue is
OL,14,Fclear in my Police and Crime Plan and
OL,15,Fthe Panel will know that I have
OL,16,Fpersonally driven a number of projects
OL,17,Fand initiatives to tackle VAWG and the
OL,18,Fcrimes that disproportionately affect
OL,19,Fwomen and girls.
